{"tid":784064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城主席揭露點解唔簽山齊士","createTime":"2018-08-18T05:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T17:44:33.000Z","uid":147522,"like":156,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"e248ff1217f62ad874995400a0cfd5e93cdc6f60","tid":784064,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"近日，曼城隊紀錄片《All or nothing》正在熱映，而在該紀錄片中，曼城主席也就球隊為何不簽入前阿仙奴球員山齊士作出回應，原因竟然只是單純覺得山齊士太貴了！<br />\n<br />\n　　曼城主席穆波歷克表示：「事實上，哥迪奧拿非常欣賞山齊士，我們在2017年就想把他帶到曼城，但那時的形勢不太好。在一月我們又嘗試與山齊士進行接觸，但是超過4,000萬英鎊的轉會費，加上球員每週50萬英鎊的工資，這實在太貴了！沒有其他原因，就是因為這個，我們沒有簽山齊士&middot;&middot;&middot;」<br />\n<br />\n　　最終的結果是，山齊士選擇加盟曼城的同城死敵曼聯，在19場比賽中攻入3球。"},{"pid":"8ed77271092218fc5ca6fb7b47d8367035d4aa4b","tid":784064,"uid":25754,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"貴囉ON9"},{"pid":"e88de5173a1b978ea52431fdac2408ab0dabe457","tid":784064,"uid":45505,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"真係500k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bfa3ae40039809ac38b5af5a213f440a79d285","tid":784064,"uid":5649,"like":74,"dislike":6,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"我地曼城小本經營，量入為出"},{"pid":"b81b1dc9721e85fa2adaa1f36f7590383bc58159","tid":784064,"uid":37566,"like":33,"dislike":8,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"e88de5173a1b978ea52431fdac2408ab0dabe457","tid":784064,"uid":45505,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"真係500k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"班狗話冇500k咁多啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cd363d28807d7debed59a368c0f45b92c56b45","tid":784064,"uid":62343,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"居然仲有人信...."},{"p